race.comment: FITZROY STREET (3) has been plying her trade in harder Sunny Coast contests and should appreciate the drop back in company here. Has placed two from three over this mile journey and a much better showing is anticipated. SOUTHAVEN (8) has been right there in all three runs this preparation and gets some weight relief with Orr's claim. Should be right there when the judge calls a halt. RUN FREDA RUN (9) has a solid record here on her home track and only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to play a role in the finish. NATIVE BEE (4) got a confidence-building win over this course and distance at the latest effort and should not be discounted lightly. WHATJEUDOIN' (7) next best with Lerena on board.
